deck: Urbanus is nog altijd smoorverliefd op juffrouw Pussy. En het lijkt wel of juffrouw Pussy ook dol is op Urbanus. Botswana en Dikke Herman kunnen het nauwelijks geloven, maar juffrouw Pussy en Urbanus zijn een stelletje. Of is hier meer aan de hand?
name: De Asielvlinders

deck: Wanneer de politie binnenvalt in de PUSSYCAT en de baas wordt gearresteerd op verdenking van belastingfraude, is dat het begin van een hele reeks gebeurtenissen. Een oude bekende van Boma maakt jacht op een doos met Bomaworst, die toevallig in een radiospelletje gewonnen wordt door Mevrouw Van de Sijpe. Er ontstaat een waanzinnige zoektocht, waarvan Fernand natuurlijk de klos is en Boma de rekening krijgt gepresenteerd.
name: Paniek in de Pussycat

description: When in Antwerp three people disappear one by one, Van de Kasseien gets flustered. Shall he be number four? Long ago, he was involved in a shady business. Why does an Indian diamond seller still want revenge after all these years? And what is the role of the old painter in this? As usual, it comes to Marcel Kiekeboe to save the day. Luckily Charlotte, Fanny and Nopel are near...
name: Wie A Zegt

description: In an attempt to save Schanulleke from drowning, Wiske is ruthlessly sucked into the water by the propellers of a ship. She gets noticed in time and is pulled out of the water, but Schanulleke is lost. Wiske is unconsolable! She is sinking into a depression. To save Wiske, her memory of her doll must be erased. According to Barabas, there is but one person who has ever achieved that and that is the Arabian alchemist Al Kimia. Our friends go look for him in the city of 's Hertogenbosch in the year 1485, where the famous painter Jheronimus Bosch is also active at that moment...
name: De Bibberende Bosch

description: A simple change of venues for one of Matt Murdock's cases becomes more complicated when The Punisher attempts to send the defendant away...permanently! If Daredevil and Blindspot want to get this mobster his day in court, it will take every ounce of wit and wile they have. All Frank needs to get what he wants is a bullet. The race is on!
name: Chapter Two

description:
With SANCTUM, Xavier Dorison and Christophe Bec have created a horrifying take on the epic battle between good and evil.

After receiving a distress call from another submarine off the coast of Syria, the crew of the U.S.S. Nebraska searches a series of massive caverns. There they discover a shipwrecked submarine - a 70-year-old Soviet sub whose crew died under mysterious circumstances.

While investigating the mystery of the sub's demise, the away team for the Nebraska discovers a massive underground sanctum dedicated to Môt, the ancient Ugarit god of death. As mysterious events start to occur onboard the Nebraska, the away team soon discovers that the sanctum was not constructed to worship Môt... it was built to imprison him. Now they must find a way to escape the death god's prison without freeing him to wreak destruction upon the world.
name: Sanctum

Spider-Man & Silk are stuck back in time with Uncle Ben...and they've tried every way they can think of to fix things. Now, they only have one unthinkable option left.
name: Chapter Five

description:
A suburban housewife with a criminal past and a thirst for adrenaline is about to get a top-secret side job: carrying out the government's most dangerous missions.

While Renear infiltrates a foreign embassy, the private detective that her husband Robert hired to track her movements amasses a dossier of photos and details of her interactions with the Handler. Will Robert's suspicions of an affair prove correct?
Calavera's adventures continue as she faces off against the deadly Necromaster and his undead empire!

When a federal agent becomes a victim of the system he has sworn to uphold, he finds true justice in the criminal underworld.

In this final chapter, the authorities have captured Philip as rival families vie for control of the Chicago underworld. Can Philip prove his innocence before his enemies silence him for good?

The first issue of the hit miniseries is reprinted at just $1.00, with pages from the DC ESSENTIALS CATALOGUE! When satellites start to fall from the sky, Superman soars into action-but the big question is: Who stopped the last one from falling!

Ghost’s past has come back to haunt him. Bone-tired and wounded, Ghost’s thirst for revenge is making him reckless. And when another Dead Mans Party "guest" arrives, that recklessness just might make Ghost dead.

As Dawson Coles continues on her quest to rid the world of the DEVIL'S CROSS GANG.

GUNNER the Texas Ranger and WHITETAIL the Native Indian Tracker are hot on her trail, and that trail is leading towards LADY ROSE current Girlfriend of the GOLD TOOTHED MAN...

DEATH-RATTLER

A Lord of the Runes has the honour of fighting for his clan. In the event of conflict or dispute, this avoids a bloodbath between the fortress-states. Two fighters, one winner, and then the conflict is over.

Redwin is a teenage Dwarf of the Order of the Forge. He wants to become the Lord of the Runes of his clan against the wishes of his father. Unable to bear the humiliation of his father being called a coward, he decides nonetheless to become Lord of the Runes by his own means. The ensuing initiation rites include not only the art of forging arms, but also that of fighting... To become a Lord of the Runes, Redwin will confront a thousand warriors, including Rom who shares the same ambition. He will lose a lot, his soul, and his father in the pursuit of his obsession.
name: Redwin of the Forge

description: Lucy's blood-drenched past is revealed when she reaches out to an "old friend" for help in finding her sister's (Jill) killer. Oberon, meanwhile, reaches out to a long-time associate of his own -- one whose involvement could spell doom for Lucy, Charli, and all of humankind.

Scrooge and the squad continue their search for answers in the penultimate chapter of 451's HUMBUG. Our kind-hearted miser on a mission keeps finding trouble around every cobblestone corner. As the House of Humbug's enemies multiply (literally), will Scrooge be able to "link" together the clues in time to save London? Find out in HUMBUG #4!

The moment everyone has been waiting for: Damian finally dons the costume of Nightwing. But what motivates him to do so—and what does he think it will accomplish? The answer may reveal itself when he encounters Catwoman, who seems to have returned to her criminal ways. Plus, Superman takes on Solomon Grundy!

volume.name: Injustice: Gods Among Us Year Five

description: The GUARDIANS OF THE GALAXY are headed to Knowhere fast! They're after shape-shifter Corhanis, who's possessed Drax's body and walked him into the meanest market in the galaxy! The Guardians may need an old friend's help on this one!

volume.name: Marvel Universe Guardians of the Galaxy Infinite Comic
